properties.Name: TransunionCollectionRecord
properties.Description: TransUnion information related to collection actions related to the consumer.

Columns.Name: CollectingCompanyName
Columns.Description: The name of the collecting company or party.

Columns.Name: OriginalCreditorName
Columns.Description: The name of the original creditor.

Columns.Name: BalanceAmount
Columns.Description: The balance amount due to be collected.

Columns.Name: PastDueAmount
Columns.Description: The total past due collections amount.

Columns.Name: LastPaymentAmount
Columns.Description: The amount of the last payment.

Columns.Name: DateOpened
Columns.Description: The date that the collection action was opened.

Columns.Name: DateClosed
Columns.Description: The date that the collection action was closed.

Columns.Name: AmountPaid
Columns.Description: The amount paid upon the collections to date.

Columns.Name: VerifiedDate
Columns.Description: The date that the data was verified.

Columns.Name: TransunionAccountTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a TransUnion account type.

Columns.Name: TransunionResponsibilityTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a TransUnion Responsibility Type.

Columns.Name: TransunionKindOfBusinessClassificationId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the TransUnion Kind Of Business Classification.
